ğŸ’¡ Solution: Revolutionary Architecture

The project introduced a 7-step autonomous feedback loop:
	1.	Generate SwiftUI code with AI (Claude/GPT)
	2.	Build via XcodeBuildMCP integration
	3.	Deploy to the iOS Simulator automatically
	4.	Capture a screenshot of the rendered UI
	5.	Run computer vision + HIG checks
	6.	Refine code based on visual analysis
	7.	Repeat until the UI meets professional standards

